        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Feature/agents directory refinement",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- **Problem**: The legacy Agents tab used a giant dropdown that was difficult to navigate with 100+ agents and lacked visual hierarchy.\r\n- **Why it matters**: Scaling to a large directory requires a searchable, card-based interface where key agents (like the Orchestrator) are prioritized and easy to find.\r\n- **What changed**: \r\n  - Implemented a card-based directory grid with search, sorting, and priority ranking.\r\n  - Assigned suitable emojis to all agents based on ID/Name and prioritized \"Mastermind\" agents.\r\n  - Cleaned up card metadata (removed workspace/runtime noise) for a premium aesthetic.\r\n  - Fixed navigation and state synchronization errors in the UI orchestration layer.\r\n- **What did NOT change**: The underlying agent configuration schema and existing detail tabs (Files, Tools, etc.) remain intact.\r\n\r\n## Change Type (select all)\r\n\r\n- [x] Bug fix\r\n- [x] Feature\r\n- [x] Refactor required for the fix\r\n- [ ] Docs\r\n- [ ] Security hardening\r\n- [ ] Chore/infra\r\n\r\n## Scope (select all touched areas)\r\n\r\n- [ ] Gateway / orchestration\r\n- [ ] Skills / tool execution\r\n- [ ] Auth / tokens\r\n- [ ] Memory / storage\r\n- [ ] Integrations\r\n- [ ] API / contracts\r\n- [x] UI / DX\r\n- [ ] CI/CD / infra\r\n\r\n## Linked Issue/PR\r\n\r\n- Closes # [Insert Issue Number here if applicable]\r\n- Related #\r\n- [x] This PR fixes a bug or regression (URL state sync error)\r\n\r\n## Real behavior proof (required for external PRs)\r\n\r\n- **Behavior or issue addressed**: Migrated from dropdown to card directory; fixed \"back button\" broken navigation.\r\n- **Real environment tested**: Local macOS Development Environment.\r\n- **Exact steps or command run after this patch**: `pnpm dev` (Control UI) -> Navigate to Agents Tab.\r\n- **Evidence after fix**: \r\n  [ADD SCREENSHOT OF CARDS HERE]\r\n  - Observed priority: Rocket-Default (1st) -> Orchestrator (2nd) -> Alphabetical.\r\n  - Observed UI: \"Primary model: openrouter/free\" on a single line.\r\n\r\n## Root Cause (if applicable)\r\n\r\n- **Root cause**: `SettingsHost` was missing optional properties present in `AppViewState`, causing type-errors during URL synchronization calls.\r\n- **Missing detection / guardrail**: Tight coupling of the directory state to the URL sync logic.\r\n\r\n## Regression Test Plan (if applicable)\r\n\r\n- **Coverage level that should have caught this**:\r\n  - [x] Unit test\r\n  - [ ] Seam / integration test\r\n  - [ ] End-to-end test\r\n- **Target test or file**: `ui/src/ui/views/agents-directory.test.ts`\r\n- **Scenario the test should lock in**: Sorting by priority (Default/Orchestrator first) and filtering by search query.\r\n\r\n## User-visible / Behavior Changes\r\n\r\n- New card-based \"Directory\" view in the Agents tab.\r\n- Removal of workspace/runtime labels from cards to reduce visual clutter.\r\n- High-priority agents (Mastermind/Orchestrator) pinned to top.\r\n\r\n## Diagram (if applicable)\r\n\r\n```text\r\nBefore:\r\n[Agents Tab] -> [Select Dropdown] -> [Choose Agent] -> [Manual Nav]\r\n\r\nAfter:\r\n[Agents Tab] -> [Search/Grid Cards] -> [Click Card] -> [Auto-Nav to Overview] -> [Back to Directory]\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Security Impact (required)\r\n\r\n- New permissions/capabilities? (`No`)\r\n- Secrets/tokens handling changed? (`No`)\r\n- New/changed network calls? (`No`)\r\n- Command/tool execution surface changed? (`No`)\r\n- Data access scope changed? (`No`)\r\n\r\n## Repro + Verification\r\n\r\n### Environment\r\n\r\n- OS: macOS\r\n- Runtime/container: Node 22+\r\n- Model/provider: OpenRouter\r\n\r\n### Steps\r\n\r\n1. Navigate to the Agents tab.\r\n2. Search for \"orchestrator\" to verify fuzzy matching.\r\n3. Click an agent card to verify deep-linking to the Detail view.\r\n4. Click the \"Back to Agents\" button to verify state reset.\r\n\r\n### Expected\r\n\r\n- Smooth transition between Directory and Detail views with correct URL updates.\r\n- Orchestrator always appearing in the top 2 slots.\r\n\r\n## Human Verification (required)\r\n\r\n- **Verified scenarios**: Card grid rendering, search filtering, priority sorting, mobile-responsiveness.\r\n- **Edge cases checked**: Search with no results, agents with no identity (fallback to ID + generic emoji).\r\n\r\n## Compatibility / Migration\r\n\r\n- Backward compatible? (`Yes`)\r\n- Config/env changes? (`No`)\r\n- Migration needed? (`No`)\r\n\r\n## Risks and Mitigations\r\n\r\n- **Risk**: Search performance with very high (>500) agent counts.\r\n  - **Mitigation**: Implemented efficient `toSorted` and `filter` logic in the view layer.\r\n<img width=\"1920\" height=\"1200\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-05-11 at 5 35 10 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f6cd0810-3e38-443e-82bf-d9699710d722\" />\r\n<img width=\"1920\" height=\"1200\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-05-11 at 6 25 54 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5d6fd754-7a84-4953-9265-d9be58a99d97\" />\r\n\r\n",
